        <p>Mobile Number:99999us999</p>
        <p>Designation:Software Engineer</p>
        <p>StartDate: 2021/01/10</p>
        <p>Department:IT Department</p>
        <p> 
            <span class="badge badge-success" 
                style="display: inline-block; padding:.5rem;">Role:Admin</span></p>

    </div>
</div>